|AddStaff|Name:"Zang"|Label:"Zang"|LabelAbbr:"ZNG"|Group:"Standard"
|StaffProperties|EndingBar:Section Close|Visible:Y|BoundaryTop:10|BoundaryBottom:18|Lines:5|WithNextStaff:ConnectBars|Color:Default
