|Lyrics|Placement:Bottom|Align:Standard Rules|Offset:0
|Lyric1|Text:"_ _ _ _ _\n_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _\n_ _ _ _ _\n_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _\n_ _ _ _ _ _\n_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _\n\nWhy in-te-gri-ty?\nWe are so suc-ces-ful af-ter all.\n\nPrin-cip-les on call:\nDo we real-ly need phi-lo-so-phy?\n\nBut take me by the hand,\nTell me which to pick and which to ban.\n"
